author: brane
msg: Move the svn_private_config.h file out of the top-level directory.
I was quite bored by its being there.
* configure.in: Generate svn_private_config.h in the subversion/ subdir.
(SVN_EXTRA_INCLUDES): Tweak the stanza pointing to svn_private_config.h.
* subversion/svn_private_config.hw: Moved here from one level above.
* build/generator/gen_win.py, build/win32/svn_config.dsp,
build/win32/svn_config.vcproj: Reflect the new location.

author: xsteve
msg: * trunk/contrib/client-side/psvn/psvn.el:
(svn-process-sentinel): Do not try to change the content of a read-only *svn-log* buffer
(svn-log-view-diff): Now use a prefix argument
- with prefix argument: ask the user for the revisions for the diff
- without the prefix argument: show the changeset for the revision at point
against that revision number minus one.

author: sussman
msg: Followup to #1818:  copy bdb tables in larger chunks.
* libsvn_fs_base/fs.c
(base_hotcopy): use the largest possible multiple of BDB's pagesize
less than SVN_STREAM_CHUNK_SIZE.  If we don't know BDB's pagesize,
default to 128K.
